{"type":null,"faqId":34565,"title":"如何设置屏幕锁？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.22222222in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p5{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>在主屏幕上，点击“设置 &gt; 锁屏和密码”，点击或滑动“锁屏”后面的开关，然后点击“锁屏密码”选择锁屏样式并根据提示进行设置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >图1-1</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=110301\" style=\"width:5.4708333in;height:2.60625in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=110302\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>所有图片仅供参考，具体操作请以实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n<br>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":166,"faqType":"显示与外观","useful":2,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9306","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-Screen-Display","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436866851000,"seriesProductName":"M2-801w,M2-803L","visitedTimes":159,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justVie